{"name":"Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Beta","instances":[],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Tactic.Grind.Types"],"declarations":[{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Beta.lean#L64-L79","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateBetaForNewApp","line":64,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Beta.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateBetaForNewApp","doc":"Applies beta-reduction for lambdas in `f`s equivalence class.\nWe use this function while internalizing new applications.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Beta.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateBetaForNewApp\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Grind</span>.<span class=\"name\">propagateBetaForNewApp</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Types.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.GoalM\">GoalM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Unit\">Unit</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Beta.lean#L34-L52","name":"Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateBetaEqs","line":34,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Beta.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateBetaEqs","doc":"For each `lam` in `lams` s.t. `lam` and `f` are in the same equivalence class,\npropagate `f args = lam args`.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Tactic/Grind/Beta.html#Lean.Meta.Grind.propagateBetaEqs\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\"